title: The proposed development shall be subject to any other conditions prescribed by the Municipal Commissioner
clause_text: The proposed development shall be subject to any other conditions prescribed by the Municipal Commissioner. Concerned land owner/development/society/company shall not be allowed to operate the public parking. Area covered under parking shall not be counted towards FSI consumption.
section: 33(18) Development of Multi Storey Public Parking Lots (PPL):

source_pdf.text_snippet: The proposed development shall be subject to any other conditions prescribed by the Municipal Commissioner.
